{"tid":1349030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去到今日你仲講「落單」，醜唔醜呀","createTime":"2019-07-22T09:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T06:09:04.000Z","uid":192824,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"daa61df05013195763e97194e94e638910591cee","tid":1349030,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:27:02.000Z","msg":"廣東話的「落單」，在不同的場景下，普通話的含意並不相同。在餐廳中是指「點菜」，也可以用於商業貿易中的「下訂單」。<br />\n「落單」在普通話是指變成孤單一個。「單」代表孤獨，形單影隻的意思，例如一隻南飛的大雁落單了，是指牠孤單地獨自飛行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/207436002773119/posts/237029339813785/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F207436002773119%2Fposts%2F237029339813785%2F&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=6251a9bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/207436002773119/posts/237029339813785/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">不要說落單，試著說跟甩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"580fb057a1e34f2f6797d3cfc77cc681cebbbe0d","tid":1349030,"uid":192824,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"例子：<br />\n<br />\n唔好落單呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好跟甩呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2bba949dd0ae8ecff11d21c58cc5d59f791937","tid":1349030,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"71ea1ad067cd7b242a5fb6c29576bc669697f6a8","tid":1349030,"uid":61798,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:33:45.000Z","msg":"唔好單丁會唔會似D"},{"pid":"1ef2ade62dd11b6cd69c512afad57d5c6525f1d9","tid":1349030,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c2bba949dd0ae8ecff11d21c58cc5d59f791937","tid":1349030,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"